MySQL StatefulSet    вҶ’ EBS (each pod own volume, same AZ)
Jenkins Master       вҶ’ EBS (single pod, persistent home)
Shared uploads       вҶ’ EFS (all webapp pods share files)
ML Model files       вҶ’ EFS (all inference pods read same model)
Logs aggregation     вҶ’ EFS (multiple pods write logs)
Config files         вҶ’ EFS (all pods read same config)

